ðŸ“¨ Text Messaging: Send and receive messages in real-time.
ðŸ–¼ï¸ File Transfers: Send and receive files (e.g., images).
ðŸ‘¥ Contact Management: Add, remove, and view contacts.
ðŸ‘€ Online Users List: Request a list of connected users.
ðŸ“© Status Notifications: Get delivery status ("delivered", "offline").
