Contact Management:

+-------------+ +-------------+ +-------------+
| Client (Alice) | Server | | Client (Bob)|
+-------------+ +-------------+ +-------------+
| 1. Send: | |
| {"type": "contact"} |----------------------------->|
| | 2. Deliver to Bob |
