Request Online Users:

+-------------+ +-------------+
| Client (Alice) | Server |
+-------------+ +-------------+
| 1. Send: |
| {"type": "online_users"} |
|----------------------------->|
| | 2. Respond: ["Alice", "Bob"]
| |<-----------------------------|
